<package version="1.0">
	<name>PHP_Compat</name>
	<summary>Provides missing functionality for older versions of PHP.</summary>

	<description>
		PHP_Compat provides missing functionality in the form of Constants and Functions for older versions of PHP.

		Constants:
		* E_STRICT
		* PATH_SEPERATOR
		* STDIN
		* STDOUT
		* STDERR
		* FILE_APPEND
		* FILE_USE_INCLUDE_PATH

		Functions:
		* file_get_contents
		* file_put_contents
		* is_a
		* scandir
		* array_combine
		* str_split
		* http_build_query
	</description>

